About Al Kifaf
Al Kifaf is a modern residential community with an eco-friendly environment. The neighbourhood has plenty of green spaces and trees, which provide ample shade for enjoying nearby landscaped areas, fountains, and ponds. The neighbourhood is located in the northern part of the Za’abeel community. It is a quaint and cosy area that offers a mix of residential and commercial buildings. Properties in the neighbourhood include apartments, townhouses, and penthouses, as well as offices and retail stores.
